Description: Provides a unified interface for computation-friendly penalized principal machine (P2PM) estimators for sufficient dimension reduction (SDR) in regression and classification. Includes state-of-the-art sparse SDR methods such as P2(W)LSM, P2(W)L2M, P2(W)LR, P2(W)SVM, P2QR, and P2AR.
